high_descs: Walk to the sink to your right.
Grab the sponge from the cabinet below.
Turn right and bring the sponge to the toilet to your right.
Place the sponge on the toilet.
Walk to the sink to your right.
Grab the sponge on top of the counter.
Turn right and bring the sponge to the toilet to your right.
Stand the sponge next the the laying sponge on the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Place sponge one and two on the toilet.

high_descs: Walk towards the shower, then stop and turn to your right at the second sink.
Pull out a green and yellow sponge from the right cabinet door, under the sink.
Turn around and walk to the toilet.
Place the sponge on the tank of the toilet, to the left of the pump bottle.
Turn around and go back to the counter between the two sinks.
Pick up the green and yellow sponge on the counter, between the two sinks.
Turn around and go back to the toilet across from you.
Place the green and yellow sponge on the tank of the toilet on the right of the other sponge, and in front of the pump bottle.
anns.task_desc: Put two sponges on the back of the toilet.

high_descs: Go to the sink on the right side.
Open the cabinet under the sink and pick up the green sponge.
Turn around and go to the left side of the toilet.
Place the sponge next to the hand soap on the top of the water tank on the toilet.
Go back to the sink on the right.
Pick up the green sponge on the top of the sink.
Go back to the left side of the toilet.
Place the sponge standing up to the right of the first sponge.
anns.task_desc: Gather the sponges and put them on the toilet water tank.
